<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Final Tax Reminder</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>We haven’t heard from you, and this is at the heart of resolving
            your case.</p>
          <p>If you’re overwhelmed, missing the organizer, or even considering
            an extension—that’s okay. Just call us. It’s a quick conversation,
            and we’ll follow up when you're ready. It’s not too late to get
            organized and file on time.</p>
          <p><strong>Please don’t file on your own without talking to us first.</strong>
            Doing so could land you right back in the same situation that
            brought you to us. Let us help you do it the right way.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us at
            <a
              href="tel:{{number}}"
              style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{number}}</a>
            and we’ll take it from there.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>